  <h2><a href="http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.polygon.com&#x2F;forums&#x2F;heroes-of-the-storm&#x2F;2015&#x2F;2&#x2F;17&#x2F;8052569&#x2F;contest-another-chance-to-get-into-the-heroes-of-the-storm-closed-beta" data-analytics-link="fanpost">Contest: Another chance to get into the Heroes of the Storm Closed&nbsp;Beta</a></h2>
